Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.31,0:00:18.34,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I have a big gun, I took it from my Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:21.79,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Sick with Justice, I just wanna feel you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:25.20,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'm your angel, only a ring away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.32,0:00:28.55,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You make me violate you, no matter who you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's all up to you, no one lives forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:42.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Been burn in the hell, by all those pigs out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.34,0:00:45.53,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}It's always been hell, from when I was born...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:48.72,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}They make me violate them, no matter who they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.72,0:00:52.26,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fs79}Get down on your knees! Get a good head on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.26,0:00:55.69,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}If it's for your guys, go to the end of the Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:59.00,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Do what you think, give it with dedication...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:02.27,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}I'll put out your misery!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.36,0:01:05.67,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}You made a mess! For Christ sakes, this rotten world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:09.10,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Shit out of luck! Go with my vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:12.54,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Light up the fire! Right on the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:15.90,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:24.48,Black Lagoon OP Credits,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Weapon... I have it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.52,0:01:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now... Okay.\NMy name is Takenaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.69,0:01:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Masahiro Takenaka.\NWhat's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.06,0:01:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem right\Nfor you to stay nameless. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't mind\Ncalling you "bro".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.58,0:02:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, baby! I didn't know\Nyou wanted to die so badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Volunteering for suicide,\Nare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.38,0:02:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you born in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was born in Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.16,0:02:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you go to Shinjuku a lot?\NOh, is L'Etoile still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they tore down\Nthe Nichigeki theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember, after a demonstration\Nmarch we had at the JNR...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I went there\Nto watch "Abashiri Bangaichi".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.98,0:02:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know it?\NIt's a film starring Mr. Ken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was following our fight with\Nthe riot police.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went there as-is, in my black helmet,\Nwar-stick outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.12,0:02:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so young back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you miss Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me ask you why you're\Ncrossing this dangerous bridge, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.80,0:02:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't imagine it's to put food\Non your plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't a lot of folks\Nwho'd do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...seeing that Japan's full of\Npetit bourgeoisies these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me, at this point...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.38,0:03:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you and I are both outsiders\Nof that country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel empathy towards you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna know why you've chosen\Nto become an adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm different from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't group me\Nwith people like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.80,0:03:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? How are you different?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.43,0:03:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't chased out or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.04,0:03:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were forced into a corner,\Nand you escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.68,0:03:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm young,\Nbut I know what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, I left Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...having gambled everything on\Nhuman activism...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and complete,\Nworldwide revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have a will and a mission,\Nit's not called losing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have anything about you\Nlike that, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a difference between us,\Nthat's where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have that sort of thing as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder. A resolution\Nand a mission are synonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about you? You don't\Nhave a mission any more, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or at least,\Nyou no longer believe in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey bro...\N- Cut it out, Takenaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.99,0:04:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I understand that this\NJapanese conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has nothing to do\Nwith the interrogation!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, listen up, Japanese guy.\NI'm not as kind as this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time.\NWhere are the documents?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.27,0:04:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- We're gonna walk from here.\N- Can't we keep driving there by car?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.77,0:04:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna charge in on them in this\Npiece of crap, with a junkie at the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you! This is the\Nworld's greatest four-wheeler, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already sick of being stuck\Nwith a drunkard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.45,0:04:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you fucking Irish.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here until you get the signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.89,0:05:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run away,\NI'll hunt you down and kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.19,0:05:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My! She says some good things!\NI agree intensely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want you drugged up\Nwhen we make a run for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's unnecessary to worry about this guy\Nwhen it comes to that, yes it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even with his brain off to Mars,\Nhis driving is never affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, "yes it is" lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you prefer your ass\Nbe split in four?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nice to make fun of others.\NYou rotten bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard this story a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about a man\Nwho came to a city.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to a street corner,\Nand all alone, he began preaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To make the world a better place"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.30,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that man kept preaching,\Nday after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.78,0:05:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first many expressed interest\Nin what the man had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some even said they would\Nfight alongside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, gradually,\Nthey all lost interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To them, it didn't matter\Nwhat happened to this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the man didn't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.73,0:06:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even as he aged, with not a single soul\Nlistening to him, he continued.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then one day, a child who was\Nwalking by asked him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,..."Why do you continue preaching\Nwhen there's nobody here?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man answered, " I thought I could\Nchange everyone in the beginning."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Then I realized that it was\Na hopeless dream."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"But the reason\NI won't stop preaching..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I won't\Nstop fighting is, bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then,\NI gambled my whole life on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't wanna have\Nthat become a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... It seems that you\Nand I really are different, bro. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much shall\Nwe hurt him, Takenaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be necessary.\NHe's not a soldier, just a delivery boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has no reason to be loyal.\NLeave him alone and he'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't talk by morning,\Nwell, we are soldiers, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to pass an informal court\Nhearing and send him to the firing squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow? Every minute that passes\Nis hurting us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the brink of determining\Nwhether or not the plan goes ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Don't you understand, Takenaka?\N- Don't be so tense, Ibraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If not him, we'll go after\Nthe girl we left at the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.79,0:07:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might just come waltzing in here\Nto save him. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three at the west gate.\NSix at the east gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only a 50-caliber at the front.\NAny mines?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. The camp is always moving.\NThat would be too much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.24,0:08:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should hurry, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.65,0:08:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your dumbass partner talks,\Nwe'd suffer a great loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.05,0:08:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.\NHe's tight-lipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't talk even if\Nthe judge's trumpets sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move in when the sun sets.\NYou ready, "yes it is" lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely. But remember,\Nwhen this is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll carve some meat off your ass.\NYou whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.54,0:08:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takenaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry for calling you,\Nbut there's something bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received the reports of the teams\Ninvestigating Thailand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other three were blanks!\NThat Japanese has the key!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your actions are interfering with the plan,\Nyou know! Takenaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:09:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... You know very well\Nwhy this is so important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What happened with the team\Nwe sent into the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't change the subject, Takenaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.97,0:09:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not changing the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many hours has it been\Nsince the search group left?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why haven't they reported back?\N- That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the surveillance team\Nat the government camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman hasn't been\Nfound anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case,\Nwhere is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Feels so good\Nyou can't pull the trigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though men know all about stabbing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they usually haven't experienced\Nbeing stabbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.24,0:09:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting started, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy! I'm in here!\NRevy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby, baby.\NHave you been a good boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you promise to behave\Na little longer, sweetie-pie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll even buy you some licorice candy.\NSo, let's get the hell outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh? Is this the dumbass?\N- Who the hell is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Rock, come up with a strategy!\N- What are you talking about? Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's a good plan!\NGet going!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaaat?\NI have no plans to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn to do your job!\NNow, get this damn thing moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.93,0:10:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I forgot!\NI must go to Liverpool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.00,0:11:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use now.\NHe's super relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimi Hendrix is calling me!\NHe's telling me to defeat the Klingons!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Picard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!\NYou're going the wrong way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being an idiot! You've brought us\Nsmack into the middle of enemy territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. Guess there's\Nno choice now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those crazy bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.57,0:11:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units! After them! Go after\Nthose guys that just came through!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get them!\NCorner them and kill them! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.91,0:11:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Rash behavior won't get you anywhere.\N- You shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.51,0:11:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, seeing that Rock\Nhasn't snapped yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I take that to mean the enemy's\Nnot much of an opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.05,0:11:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that. Those fools are\Ncoming after us in herds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Damn it!\N- I understand how you feel, but Ibraha...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.23,0:12:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a mission I've been\Ntrying to accomplish for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that damn gangster ruin it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. Damn. Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?\NHere they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revy. I talked\Nto that Japanese guy. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost, damn it!\NI get leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.85,0:12:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn after you take out two cars!\NDid you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.13,0:12:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!\NI'm gonna fly now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What are you doing?!\N- Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You idiot!\NI said don't kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The left! I get the left,\Nyou take the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!\NThere's no room up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spread out! Watch out so you don't\Nhit any obstacles! After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rachel Welch and Jane Fonda\Nare in a footrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh. Really.\N- Stay down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- You're in my way!\N- Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.54,0:13:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world\Nare you luring me to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.87,0:13:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary nudist beach?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.81,0:13:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dutch, there are only thirty minutes\Nuntil the time limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you able to keep\Nyour ass relaxed in your seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.82,0:13:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not really. You're free to use any\Nmeans necessary. That's fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me, Mr. CIA. Yeah,\Nright on schedule. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out with your lousy jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.34,0:13:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about the money?\NI don't take American Express.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know when you get it. Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.01,0:14:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- What did Hong Kong say?\N- Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You may take the law into your\Nown hands as deemed necessary."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just don't let things get too dirty."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,\Navoid fighting them head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.09,0:14:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a tall order.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, for now all we can do\Nis wish the delivery boys luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start over!\NRock, Paper, Scissors again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't got time for that.\NHere they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.51,0:14:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Barbarella's holding up\Nan anti-war placard in the nude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll kill them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.95,0:14:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they have too much range on us\Nfor your weapon. Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I've got no choice.\NLet's see what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.02,0:14:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smartass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll make your eyes roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she's not all talk, I see.\NNice going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we had an M72 or a M242 this\Nwould have been a lot easier to finish off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid. Cannons and guns\Nrun out of ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the blade and body\Nnever malfunction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're the best weapons\Nin the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.66,0:15:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be dumb. Knives can chip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guns over swords.\NNuclear bombs over guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if we had one of those,\Nit would be awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're designed so that only\Npoliticians can get their hands on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.78,0:15:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong\Nwith your head, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.98,0:15:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bakery will sell you bread. Criminals\Nonly use such weapons for criminal acts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Peace Work is only open\Nto the first three people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break. Rock.\NHave some of this. It'll calm you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Go after them\Nwith all the base's vehicles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:16:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you cross the DMZ border,\Ndon't hesitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Charge in\Nand get the documents!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Stop it! The troops will all die!\N- Give that back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.04,0:16:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibraha! We have a job to do! Ibraha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.54,0:16:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibraha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.71,0:16:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know it! No matter what you do,\Nor how you do things...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your son is never coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DMZ, right?! The camp should be\Nvisible any time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.39,0:16:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling, Rock?\NHaving fun yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it? Running away\Nlike this always makes it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I've been running away\Nlike this since kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- It's over.\N- Oh, it's affected him the wrong way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.08,0:16:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, I screwed up. He's such a\Npositive guy, so I thought he'd be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not enough. The mood\Nat the time is just as important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I talked to the old guy\NI acted high and mighty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.42,0:17:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think about it,\NI tend to blab all I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then talk myself outta\Nthe situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go again.\NWhat is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Playmates! There are one hundred\NPlaymates, starting from 1990!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an attack of the Playmates Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.41,0:17:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! An unknown vehicle\Nhas entered the DMZ! Permission to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Number Three Bunker!{\i0}\N{\i1}That's a guest! Do not fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.38,0:17:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All bunkers and guards!{\i0}\N{\i1}That is not the enemy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is not a profession.\NIt's our way of life, isn't it, Takenaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.43,0:17:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are times when\Nwe cannot give in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.53,0:17:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ibraha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scoundrels in Jerusalem and\Nthose that protect them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...are all finally within reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show them what the Red Cross\Ncamp in Beirut was like in '87!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.97,0:17:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've come this far!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Commander! Orders, please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep after the enemy!\NCharge into the government camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must retreat! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose focus on our goal\Nbecause of our cause!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Because of our cause," Takenaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.15,0:18:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that the whole reason\Nwe've been fighting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that why you came\Nto the Beqaa Valley?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.80,0:18:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Takenaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To all units. Retreat from\Nyour present positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.78,0:18:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not return to camp. Make your way\Nto the secondary gathering point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and I were both\Nonly looking at our past.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.29,0:18:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we kept doing so,\Nnothing ever changed. But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.26,0:18:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although none of it matters now,\Nyou were a good comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a tragic story,\Ndon't you think, Ibraha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:18:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the launderer's\Ndelivery boy arrived yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Langley boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Langley's been busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are too many bastards\Nshitting on freedom and justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's this thing\Nthat's supposed to get us excited?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Crap! The briefcase!\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.69,0:19:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the briefcase!\NRevy! We're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.73,0:19:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't panic. If Harry Houdini\Nrubs the magic lamp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!\NJust like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.84,0:19:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did we have\Nto save this dumbass?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys wouldn't have agreed to come\Nunless I said he had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all wrinkled and sweaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.05,0:19:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then! Thanks! Next time, deliver it\Nin a more decent manner, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise the boss will be pissed!\NOh, and Miss Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the chief at Buffalo Hill and the NYPD\N27th Precinct heard about you now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.36,0:19:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they'd shit their pants!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.90,0:19:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job is to destroy enemies\Nof the United States!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not being paid\Nto chase criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.74,0:20:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a little something\Nfor you to think about...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...for someday when we bring you\Nyour next job! Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Revy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't thanked you yet. Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.93,0:20:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.13,0:20:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be so formal\Nwith each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.53,0:20:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Rock...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you\Nbabbling about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never doing you any favors\Nlike that again, you pea brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All costs associated with rescuing you\Nare coming outta your paycheck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna be saved again, next time\Nyou'd better ask God to do the favors!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.89,0:20:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Mr. Ken.\NWhat a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello, Mr. "Excuse Me".\NHow was your vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.16,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a great time.\NHow did things go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, it was a pain. The trade\Nfell through, and I hurt my hip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I ended up leaving a\Nclose friend after having a fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I even tried pushing what\NI couldn't accomplish onto the young.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was one unpleasant situation after\Nanother. I feel like I'm getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there'll be a next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, there'll always be\Na next time, until I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will always\Nbe a next time. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.70,0:21:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, mister,\Nwhat is it you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.63,0:21:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.84,0:21:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. Yeah, it's finally\Nclear to me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.74,0:21:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My job is to be\Nan enemy of the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:18.52,Black Lagoon Next Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur10\pos(980,916)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vampires?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those words have something\Nto do with vampires.
